Call building block from Microsoft Word dedicated company templates.

How it's made. For each building block from company template is set "autotext" feature. After entering "autotext" dedicated to specific building block F3 key has to be pressed. Next building block is inserted into document content. This library is active / working only when: 1. Microsoft Word is open. 2. Active document is based on company template.

column1: All definitions from within this library start with "@" and all have set * feature (immediate execute).
